{"tid":1509944,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Mina被診斷為不安障礙，日後行程將會有選擇的參加","createTime":"2019-08-27T04:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T08:12:46.000Z","uid":74065,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3206761aee0d7f8fbf8c42a67064e2931cc6f439","tid":1509944,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:09:35.000Z","msg":"您好，這裡是JYPE。<br />\n<br />\n向您進一步介紹Mina的健康狀況。<br />\n<br />\n經多家專業醫療機構確認，目前Mina被確診為不安障礙。該症狀的特徵是毫無預兆的發生持續性或者間歇性的極度不安狀態，不安狀態的程度也突然變動。 <br />\n<br />\nMina以後的日程參與將以這種可變情況為前提，通過Mina本人和成員們的商議進行判斷和決定。而且Mina的日程參與絕對要根據本人的客觀健康狀態，不可避免會有部分選擇性，敬請粉絲諒解。<br />\n<br />\n我司為了Mina的恢復將繼續採取最好的措施。希望大家多多支持和關心Mina。<br />\n<br />\n繼續有工開太好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49174ef43ffa911ede07ee834f7f910634066425","tid":1509944,"uid":286964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:09:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左今天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"30f842e8eeecf765d340acc1fd8c5e695b9adaf0","tid":1509944,"uid":33930,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQriHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=e23fa3ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuc